Skid Row is an area of Downtown Los Angeles east of San Pedro Street, south of Third Street, west of Central Avenue, and north of Seventh Street (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skid_Row,_Los_Angeles). For images of the skid row area in Los Angeles, see http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Los_Angeles_Skid_Row.jpg and http://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/31/us/31skidrow.html?_r=0. - Mod.ML

